-- Virginia Surgeon Avoids Prison for Conspiring to Hide HSBC Cash From IRS
-- David Voreacos
-- 2010-06-15T18:27:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/virginia-surgeon-avoids-prison-for-conspiring-to-hide-hsbc-cash-from-irs.html

          
          
             A Virginia surgeon avoided prison
after admitting he hid assets at HSBC Holdings Plc from U.S. tax
authorities and smuggled $211,200 in cash to his home when the
bank said it would close his Swiss bank account.  
